Get stanfit summary table of all parameters excluding log_lik.

Source: R/bpc_exports.R
get_stanfit_summary.Rd

Important to investigate the neff and the Rhat from the MCMC This excludes the log_lik paramter

get_stanfit_summary(bpc_object)

Arguments

bpc_object

a bpc object

Value

a data frame with the summary including quantiles, Rhat and neff

Examples

# \donttest{
m<-bpc(data = tennis_agresti,
player0 = 'player0',
player1 = 'player1',
result_column = 'y',
model_type = 'bt',
solve_ties = 'none')
